SEARCH
Module org.postgresql.pljava.internal
Package org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc

Class SQLChunkIOOrder

java.lang.Object
org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc.SQLChunkIOOrder
class SQLChunkIOOrder extends Object
Caches the scalar and mirror MappedUDT byte orders as determined by system properties during PL/Java startup.

This class is initialized from native code ahead of the SQLInputFromChunk and SQLOutputToChunk classes that depend on it. This happens before InstallHelper has taken and frozen its defensive copy of the Java system properties, and also before PL/Java user code has potentially run and changed them.

This defensive implementation is needed only for the "PL/Java with no security policy enforcement" case, as PL/Java's supplied policy file protects these properties from modification when policy is being enforced.
